The '''''Starmaster''''' was a freighter the size of a [[Victory-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Victory''-class Star Destroyer]]. It was used by [[Rol'Waran]] and [[Crev Bombaasa/Legends|Crev Bombaasa]] to smuggle [[Spice/Legends|spice]] for the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]].

